description:
Sonic Syndicate is a melodic death metal/metalcore band from Falkenberg, Sweden.





Current members

    * Richard Sjunnesson - Vocals (2002 - )
    * Roland Johansson - Vocals (2006 - )
    * Roger Sjunnesson - Lead guitar (2002 - )
    * Robin Sjunnesson - Rhythm guitar (2002 - )
    * Karin Axelsson - Bass guitar, Vocals (on Eden Fire) (2004 - )
    * John Bengtsson - Drums (2006 - )

Albums

    * 2005    Eden Fire
    * 2007    Only Inhuman
    * 2008    Love and Other Disasters
